k\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 25, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104rqe1665703206044.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/rqe1665703206044.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/rqe1665703206044.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"rqe1665703206044\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Adds a namespace to the beginning of an element tag.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"rqe1665703206044__topic_d136607e1_d136608e1_d136609e1\">\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" id=\"rqe1665703206044__codeblock_osn_hch_hwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">ADDPREFIXMAPPING (Prefix,URI</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rqe1665703206044__section_qkd_3ch_hwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1163286e56\">Parameters</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"4\" id=\"rqe1665703206044__table_d16295e1_d16296e1_d16297e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">ADDPREFIXMAPPING parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rqe1665703206044__table_d16295e1_d16296e1_d16297e1__entry__1\">Parameter</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rqe1665703206044__table_d16295e1_d16296e1_d16297e1__entry__2\">Data Type</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rqe1665703206044__table_d16295e1_d16296e1_d16297e1__entry__3\">Direction</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rqe1665703206044__table_d16295e1_d16296e1_d16297e1__entry__4\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rqe1665703206044__table_d16295e1_d16296e1_d16297e1__entry__1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">Prefix</var></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rqe1665703206044__table_d16295e1_d16296e1_d16297e1__entry__2\">String</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rqe1665703206044__table_d16295e1_d16296e1_d16297e1__entry__3\">IN</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rqe1665703206044__table_d16295e1_d16296e1_d16297e1__entry__4\">Namespace identifier prefixed to element name;\n                        maximum length is 40 bytes.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rqe1665703206044__table_d16295e1_d16296e1_d16297e1__entry__1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">URI</var></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rqe1665703206044__table_d16295e1_d16296e1_d16297e1__entry__2\">String</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rqe1665703206044__table_d16295e1_d16296e1_d16297e1__entry__3\">IN</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rqe1665703206044__table_d16295e1_d16296e1_d16297e1__entry__4\">URL or other URI for the namespace; maximum\n                        length is 512 bytes.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rqe1665703206044__section_syr_qch_hwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1163286e133\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rqe1665703206044__p_d136619e1_d136620e1_d136621e1\">Call the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">ADDPREFIXMAPPING</span>\n            operation after calling the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">STARTELEMENT</span> operation or another\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">ADDPREFIXMAPPING</span> operation.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rqe1665703206044__p_d136622e1_d136623e1_d136624e1\">The prefix defined with it does not have to be the\n            same one used in the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">STARTELEMENT</span> invocation. Thus, if the\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">STARTELEMENT</span> itself added a namespace specification, then\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">ADDPREFIXMAPPING</span> will add a second (or third or fourth …) to the\n            tag.</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104rqe1665703206044_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"rqe1665703206044__codeblock_rqv_vch_hwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">variables\n handle writer\nendvariables\nnewinstance \"UXMLWRITER\", writer\nwriter-&gt;startdocument(...)\n...\nwriter-&gt;startelement(\"p\", \"tag\", \"http://a/a/a\") ; result: &lt;p:tag\nwriter-&gt;addprefixmapping(\"s\", \"http://b/c/e\") ; result: &lt;p:tag\nwriter-&gt;addprefixmapping(\"\", \"http://a/b/default\") ; result: &lt;p:tag xmlns=\"http://a/b/default\"\n...\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vtr1665703208047.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>STARTELEMENT</a><p>Operation activated by the SAX parser when a start tag is encountered.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531741\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531741\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "ADDPREFIXMAPPING Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 25, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Adds a namespace to the beginning of an element tag. ADDPREFIXMAPPING (Prefix,URI Copy Parameters Table 1. ADDPREFIXMAPPING parameters Parameter Data Type Direction Description Prefix String IN Namespace identifier prefixed to element name; maximum length is 40 bytes. URI String IN URL or other URI for the namespace; maximum length is 512 bytes. Description Call the ADDPREFIXMAPPING operation after calling the STARTELEMENT operation or another ADDPREFIXMAPPING operation. The prefix defined with it does not have to be the same one used in the STARTELEMENT invocation. Thus, if the STARTELEMENT itself added a namespace specification, then ADDPREFIXMAPPING will add a second (or third or fourth …) to the tag. Explain this code variables handle writer endvariables newinstance \"UXMLWRITER\", writer writer->startdocument(...) ... writer->startelement(\"p\", \"tag\", \"http://a/a/a\") ; result: <p:tag writer->addprefixmapping(\"s\", \"http://b/c/e\") ; result: <p:tag writer->addprefixmapping(\"\", \"http://a/b/default\") ; result: <p:tag xmlns=\"http://a/b/default\" ... Copy Related Links STARTELEMENT Operation activated by the SAX parser when a start tag is encountered. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}